Title: AMERICAN WATER CAPITAL CORP. OFFICERS' CERTIFICATE DECEMBER 15, 2010 6.00% SENIOR MONTHLY NOTES DUE 2040 PURSUANT TO SECTIONS 102 AND 301 OF THE INDENTURE IDENTIFIED BELOW Governing Law: New York      Date: 12/15/2010 Industry: Water Utilities        Sector: Utilities









